                "key": "Aeon Wave",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>HP is increased by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">16%/20%/24%/28%/32%</span>. When current HP increases or decreases, Charged Attack DMG will be increased by<span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\"> 14%/18%/22%/26%/30%</span> for 4s. Max 3 stacks. This effect can be triggered once every 0.3s. When the character has 3 stacks or a third stack's duration refreshes, <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">8/9/10/11/12 </span>Energy will be restored. This Energy restoration effect can be triggered once every 12s.</p>"
                ]
